            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[伤心]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/l_shangxin-49b2fe44a6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%A7%B0%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E4%B8%80%E5%85%8B%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E9%87%8D%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%90%A8%E6%B2%BB%E7%96%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%A7%B0%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E4%B8%80%E5%85%8B%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E9%87%8D%E4%BA%8E%E4%B8%80%E5%90%A8%E6%B2%BB%E7%96%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#代表称心理健康一克预防重于一吨治疗#</span></a>】根据《2022年国民抑郁症蓝皮书》，18岁以下的抑郁症患者占总人数的30%，其中50%的抑郁症患者为在校学生。高压的环境、繁杂的信息，让三观未成熟的孩子更容易产生抑郁情绪，不加以干预，便会转为心理问题。当下，未成年人的心理健康存在多方面问题：难发现、不重视、不专业、不敢看、没处看......<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%AE%B6%E6%A0%A1%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E6%8E%A5%E4%BD%8F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%AD%A9%E5%AD%90%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%AE%B6%E6%A0%A1%E8%A6%81%E4%B8%80%E8%B5%B7%E6%8E%A5%E4%BD%8F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#孩子心理问题家校要一起接住#</span></a> 今年两会，多位代表和委员提出，“家校医社”的心理健康联动服务机制，一环都不能少。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E4%B8%A4%E4%BC%9A%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E5%86%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%83%AD%E6%90%9C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%BF%99%E4%BA%9B%E4%B8%A4%E4%BC%9A%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E5%86%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%83%AD%E6%90%9C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#这些两会建议冲上热搜#</span></a>（央视网）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hno6x38urlj20u018gqb3.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hno6xa4ewmj20u025sapb.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hno6x3qk8aj20u01o0k1d.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hno6x82ujwj20u024odta.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hno6xacoclj20u02y4trn.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hno6x8d9nfj20u02a8174.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hno6x2ulwej20u019011j.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hno6x4v7qsj20u01pzqe9.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hno6xcbfejj20u03id4qp.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
