            <title><![CDATA[【[举手]答网友问：#罕见病用药难费用贵怎么办#】全国人大代表、全国政协委员纷纷支招：①建立健全基层罕见病社会保障体系，加强各领域罕见病诊疗协作，发起网上...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[举手]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/fd/2022_raisehand_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>答网友问：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BD%95%E8%A7%81%E7%97%85%E7%94%A8%E8%8D%AF%E9%9A%BE%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8%E8%B4%B5%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BD%95%E8%A7%81%E7%97%85%E7%94%A8%E8%8D%AF%E9%9A%BE%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8%E8%B4%B5%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#罕见病用药难费用贵怎么办#</span></a>】全国人大代表、全国政协委员纷纷支招：①建立健全基层罕见病社会保障体系，加强各领域罕见病诊疗协作，发起网上多学科会诊；②增加诊疗资源，打造国家罕见病临床诊疗中心；③鼓励国内企业生产罕见病特医食品，倒逼进口价格下降。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%A4%E4%BC%9A%E4%BD%A0%E6%88%91%E4%BB%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#两会你我他#</span></a><br><blockquote> - 转发 <a href="https://weibo.com/2656274875" target="_blank">@央视新闻</a>: <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%A4%E4%BC%9A%E4%BD%A0%E6%88%91%E4%BB%96%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#两会你我他#</span></a>【答网友问：<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%BD%95%E8%A7%81%E7%97%85%E7%94%A8%E8%8D%AF%E9%9A%BE%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8%E8%B4%B5%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%BD%95%E8%A7%81%E7%97%85%E7%94%A8%E8%8D%AF%E9%9A%BE%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%A8%E8%B4%B5%E6%80%8E%E4%B9%88%E5%8A%9E%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#罕见病用药难费用贵怎么办#</span></a>】全国人大代表、全国政协委员纷纷支招：①建立健全基层罕见病社会保障体系，加强各领域罕见病诊疗协作，发起网上多学科会诊；②增加诊疗资源，打造国家罕见病临床诊疗中心；③鼓励国内企业生产罕见病特医食品，倒逼进口价格下降。<br><br>今年<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%A4%E4%BC%9A%23&amp;isnewpage=1" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#两会#</span></a>，你关心什么话题？上央视新闻客户端看专家答网友问→<a href="https://m.cctvnews.cctv.com/act/info-collection/index.html?campCode=562698964210553856&amp;bizCode=562698964210553856" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a> <a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E5%A4%AE%E8%A7%86%E6%96%B0%E9%97%BB">@央视新闻</a> <a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%8B%E5%A3%B0">@中国之声</a> <a href="https://weibo.com/n/%E6%80%BB%E5%8F%B0%E7%8E%AF%E7%90%83%E8%B5%84%E8%AE%AF">@总台环球资讯</a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5010494717886514" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a></blockquote><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hnm8hhpp4zj60yd0jckb702.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/pdTR41Rwlx08dbn6HFMQ01041200Mv3L0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710263768&amp;ssig=thhkgOzKwk&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/Ffx4pBsrlx08dbn5tgre01041200odTt0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710263768&amp;ssig=WzpB2e%2Fmj6&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/HT2eOFs3lx08dbn4Nz3W01041200fCi90E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710263768&amp;ssig=l0kS1hcLAc&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5010494717886514" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
